<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/19670343-thy-gold-to-refine"><img alt="Thy Gold to Refine (The Work and the Glory #4)" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1462626864l/19670343._SY75_.jpg" />
